content: Head back up the main path to find the Upper Hollow Shrine as you finally take in the breadth of this new region. Unlike the village above, this sprawling area just goes deeper and deeper underground, and is full of alternate pathways and twisting passages leading to the lower levels. Be sure to also check your weapons to craft a new Chitin Staff from defeating The Second Sister.

The content is as follows:
Head back up the main path to find the Upper Hollow Shrine as you finally take in the breadth of this new region. Unlike the village above, this sprawling area just goes deeper and deeper underground, and is full of alternate pathways and twisting passages leading to the lower levels. Be sure to also check your weapons to craft a new Chitin Staff from defeating The Second Sister.
